### AI-Ready Documentation

This project includes AI-friendly endpoints:

| Endpoint | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `/llms.txt` | Summary with documentation links for LLM context |
| `/llms-full.txt` | Complete documentation in plain text for RAG |
| `/docs/*.mdx` | Per-page Markdown access (append `.mdx` to any doc URL) |

**Page Actions**: Each documentation page includes buttons to:
- Copy page content as Markdown for LLMs
- View raw `.mdx` content
- View source on GitHub

**Content Negotiation**: AI agents can request Markdown by setting `Accept: text/markdown` header.

