### Mermaid Diagrams

Create diagrams directly in Markdown using fenced code blocks:

````markdown
```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{Decision}
    B -->|Yes| C[Action]
    B -->|No| D[End]
```
````

Supports flowcharts, sequence diagrams, entity-relationship diagrams, Gantt charts, and more.

