### Live Code Playground

Add `live` to JSX code blocks for interactive editing:

````markdown
```jsx live
function Demo() {
  const [count, setCount] = useState(0);
  return (
    <button onClick={() => setCount(c => c + 1)}>
      Clicked {count} times
    </button>
  );
}
```
````

