### Client-Side Redirects

Handle URL changes gracefully. Edit `docusaurus.config.ts`:

```typescript
plugins: [
  [
    '@docusaurus/plugin-client-redirects',
    {
      redirects: [
        { from: '/old-path', to: '/new-path' },
        { from: '/docs/v1/intro', to: '/docs/intro' },
      ],
    },
  ],
],
```

{%- endif %}

